##One foot, one spring

WECHAT denganqing1984

Features, here, I will share my writing, reading the book.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
(I)
Go to the field to see how the rape flowers grow and take a walk.
Mother picked a lot of wild vegetables, I let her listen to the sound of frogs.
"You don't hear it at night, " she laughs. "It's like an old man who can't stop talking. Nobody understands it. "
"I heard it, " I said, "and I ran out to listen. The moonlight was miles away, and I stood on the balcony and listened for a while. "
Mother asked: "You are not afraid of the cold! This son is good to hear? "
I said: "later back to Beijing, in the downtown, you will not hear. "

(II)
Mother was on the balcony, the sun was shining.
I said, "you have a lot of flowers on your shoes. "
Mother laughed: "This is called a foot of a spring. "

(III)
In the vegetable garden the turnips are plentiful, the mother pulled up several big ones.
Wash clean cut into cubes, I took a taste, sweet and delicious, juicy full, slightly spicy flavor.
The dried turnips were mixed with chilli and then placed in jars.
Daily eat porridge, often out to eat a little.
She said she could take it with her when she went back to Beijing.

(D)
I was walking with my mother when I suddenly stopped.
I pointed to the clouds in the sky and said: "The color of the clouds is pretty, light blue. "
Mother squinted for a moment. "It's nice to look at, but it's out of reach. "
I said, "when the clouds turn to rain, you will reach them. "
Mother smiled: "That lets me enough, I also not enough. Wet, I also WANT TO CHANGE CLOTHES! "

(V)
Mother called me, I was squatting on the Ridge to shoot plants.
She came over and I told her to hold still. "I'll take your picture! "
The mother flustered ground says: "I want to comb a head, change a dress. "
I said: "Do not wear out, now several good! "
Mother said: "You pat me every day, Pat a son Ghost Oh! "
I said, "I do. "
